# <type>(<scope>): <subject>     # ≤72 chars, lowercase
#
# <body>                          # WHY, not WHAT. Wrap at 72.
#
# Refs: #<issue>
#
# Allowed types:
#   build, chore, ci, docs, feat, fix, perf, refactor, revert, style, test
#
# Example:
#   feat(skills): support custom update_section in frontmatter
#
#   Skills with outcome_metrics: true can now specify which markdown
#   section the iteration loop should replace, defaulting to the
#   existing "## Reference Data".
